(4, 'Wilton Extra-Fine Foodwriter Markers 5/Pkg-Yellow/Green/Red/Blue/Black', 'Food Writer Set. It\'s a fast, fun way to add colorful designs to all kinds of baked treats! Use a FoodWriter Edible Color Marker just as you would an ink marker. Draw fun designs on cakes, write messages on cookies, or add highlights to icing decorations. This package includes 5 markers: brown, red, blue, green, and black.', 8.05, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/414Pdq799SL._SY300_.jpg', 'Wilton'),
(5, 'Skyline Furniture Velvet Tufted King Wingback Headboard, Buckwheat', 'This stylish tufted headboard is a great way to redesign your bedroom. It features deep hand-pulled tufts and eye-catching wings. Easily attaches to standard metal bed frames. Requires a box spring and mattress (not included).', 526.5, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41M49%2B7Qb0L._SX300_.jpg', NULL),
