(7, 'Taiwon Metal Stainless Steel Modern Space pattern flatware, Demitasse Spoon set of 12', 'Modern Space is very simple and classy pattern of Taiwon Metal Industry. This pattern became one of the most widely used patterns since 2003. Designer got inspiration from space and its mystique. Comes in a set of 12 Demitasse Spoon - 4.6 Inches long***Material Information***18/10 and 18/0 is not the same quality of material used and vary considerably in price and composition. Stainless flatware that is 18/10 means that the material is consist of 18% chromium and 10% nickel. Similarly, 18/8 is 8% ofickel and 18/0 is 0%. The higher the nickel content, the more protection the flatware has from corrosion. Water and dishwasher detergents tend to be harsh to stainless steel flatware and that can sometimes cause blemishes. These can often be removed with a stainless steel cleanser but pitting, chipping or rusting sometimes cannot be removed. 18/10 and 18/8 are protective for rust, and these usually last much longer than 18/0.', 22.95, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41mRYjY7e-L._SX300_.jpg', NULL),
(8, 'SilverStone2 Webster Place 10-Piece Cookware Set, Pomegranate', 'The perfect set for today\'s adventurous chef.  You get a 1 quart and a 1.5 quart covered saucepan, a 4 quart covered saucepot, a 10\" skillet, and 3 tools--just the basic pieces you need in a sophisticated color you\'ll love.  Platinum colored nonstick surfaces and porcelain enamel exteriors make cleanup a snap.  Glass lids let you monitor your cooking while sealing in moisture and nutrients.', 5.88, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41XSW0DPH5L._SY300_.jpg', NULL),
(9, 'HIC Brands that Cook Nylon Mesh Strainer, 7-Inch', 'This mesh strainer is made of non-reactive nylon; it will not retain tastes, odors and will not impart flavors on foods. The convenient 7-inch diameter has many kitchen and household uses. Unique handles on sides of strainer allows the strainer to hook on the side of a pot or bowl to hold the strainer in place while straining - perfect for mess free straining and one handed use. The handle features a convenient eyelet for creative storage solutions.', 6.61, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/31fsZeD7kPL._SY300_.jpg', 'HIC Brands That Cook'),
