(11, 'Ideal Wine and Champagne Bucket - Stainless Steel', 'Stainless steel chiller with a premium polished finish.  Flanged rim adds to this item\'s elegant appearance.  4mm side carrying-rings are constructed of polished stainless steel for extra carrying strength.    Dimensions: 8.25\'\' Height x 8.25\'\' Diameter', 4.63, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41dLClw2SuL._SY300_.jpg', NULL),
(12, 'BRAND NEW Memory Foam Mattress Cover LUXURY JACQUARD VELOUR ALL AROUND ZIPPERED COVER for 10&quot; QUEEN Memory Foam Mattress', 'You are buying a BRAND NEW QUEENN Size (60\" x 80\") All Around Zippered Washable Luxury JACQUARD VELOUR COVER with Non Skid Bottom for 10\" THICK Memory Foam Mattress. This cover can be used to replace Tempurpedic mattress cover.', 6.24, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41d3gKR3kkL._SX300_.jpg', NULL),
(13, 'Chicken (Hen) and Chick Throw Pillow, Hooked, 18 Inches X 18 Inches, Red, Black, White, Tan', 'Beautifully hooked pillow.', 59.99, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51CmTkgORuL._SY300_.jpg', NULL),
(14, 'Fox Run Classic Scale Kitchen Timer, Black', 'Keep your cookies, cakes, roasts and casseroles from burning with the Fox Run Classic Scale Kitchen Timer.  The retro styling of this timer is a classic and will look great in any kitchen.  The timer can be set for a maximum of 60 minutes.', 4.99, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/513xC9oA38L._SY300_.jpg', 'Fox Run'),
(15, 'Neatnix Ready 2 Go Small Tech Organizer', 'The Ready 2 Go Tech Organizer is a lightweight portable carrier for todays small electronics, cords and accessories. Inside, the removable inner board\'s two sets of elastic straps separate earbuds, power cords, adaptors, mice, etc. They eliminate the tangling that occurs in other pouches and pockets.', 20.93, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41ZMDqqVvKL._SY300_.jpg', NULL),
(16, 'Roll Top Home Office Computer Desk in Cherry Finish by Coaster Furniture', 'The Roll Top Home Office Desk by Coaster is made from select hardwoods and veneers. This beautiful cherry finish roll top desk features a drop front keyboard drawer, removable shelves for CPU space with air ventilation antiqued brass finish hardware and locking file cabinet. This multi functional piece of furniture will help to organize your office and its warm color will blend with any decor! Dimensions: Desk: 54L x 29W x 51-3/4H', 14.72, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/512Y5XhxkcL._SX300_.jpg', NULL),
(17, 'Old Dutch Half Round Pot Rack, Graphite', 'Ideal for tight cooking areas, this half-round pot rack from  Old Dutch is a space-efficient way to keep pots handy and leave  headroom in small kitchens. The plated steel frame is lightweight but  strong and features a three-point wall-mount construction. Spacious in  grid and perimeter, it gives you plenty of options for hanging your  pots, pans, and utensils. Removable for cleaning, the grid also  provides storage for lids and bowls. All 12 hooks--six straight and six  angled--are movable to accommodate an evolving cookware collection.  Both chip- and rust-resistant, the matte graphite finish cleans up with  a damp cloth. Assembly of this rack is simple&#x97;we had it together in  just a few minutes.--Emily Bedard', 61.64, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/31jdUgjgVML._SX300_.jpg', 'OLDG9'),
(18, 'Organize It All 2-Tier Mahogany Stackable Shoe Rack', 'Shoes, shoes, shoes! Organize your shoes with this shoe rack. It\'s durable and won\'t break easily. It will hold shoes, boots, tennis shoes, clogs, and just about any other type of shoe that you can think of. This is your perfect shoe storage solution.', 84.99, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51MZiOwrQ9L._SX300_.jpg', 'Organize It All'),
(19, 'KitchenAid KTT340PK Pink 2-Slice Polycarbonate Toaster', 'General Brand KitchenAid Name 2-Slice Polycarbonate Toaster Model KTT340PK Feature Features Number of Shade Settings: 9 Even-Heat System Baker\\\'s Bagel Toasting Function Warm Function Housing Material: Polycarbonate Easy Lift Lever Soft Rise System Feature Self-Centering Bread Racks Stainless Steel Interior Hard, high-luster polycarbonate housing stays cool to the touch during use and resists stains, fingerprints and warping Extra-long, extra-wide toasting slots easily handle the thickest bagels, specialty breads and toaster pastries Full-width, stainless steel crumb tray removes easily and is dishwasher safe Power cord neatly wraps into the base of the toaster for tidy storage Spec Number of Slices 2 Slices Bagel Function Yes Crumb Tray Yes Color Pink Dimensions & Weight Height 7.59\" Width 10.22\" Depth 5.78\"', 8.01, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/21qIwKzuFSL.jpg', NULL),
(20, 'Oneida 4 Piece Measuring Spoon Set, Stainless Steel/Black', 'Oneida\'s 4 Piece Measuring Spoon Set has brushed 18/8 stainless steel and 1Tbsp., 1 tsp., 1/2 tsp., and 1/4 tsp. measurements. It has a black ABS hanging ring.', 10.86, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41lhtJafnhL._SY300_.jpg', NULL),
(21, 'Handcrafted Metal Butterfly Magnets', 'This product is made from stamped steel with a patina applied by hand. A durable clear coat has been applied to protect the finish. Industrial strength magnets have been affixed with a strong two-part epoxy for long life and durability. This product has been hand crafted in the USA. Large butterfly measures  7\"x5\" and small butterfly measures 4.5\"x2.65\".', 13.54, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41oE%2BEVLR2L._SX300_.jpg', NULL),
(22, 'Golden State Warriors Logo Basketball Poster', 'Golden State Warriors - Logo - NBAImage Size 22\" x 34\"Paper Size 22\" x 34\"', 7.33, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41qo9RneJiL._SY300_.jpg', 'Trends International'),
(23, 'NewAir AF-321-BL Scratch &amp; Dent Portable Swamp Cooler', 'When the weather heats up, enjoy cool comfort that\'s truly fresh with the NewAir AF-320 evaporative swamp cooler. This innovative swamp cooler combines evaporative cooling technology with an ionic air purifier that eliminates airborne contaminants including dust, pollen, and other allergens. The AF-320 evaporative swamp cooler features three fan speeds and covers areas up to 200 square feet, for unbeatable comfort in any room of your home or office. Oscillating louvers ensure thorough, even distribution of cool air. Lightweight and portable, this evaporative swamp cooler comes with wheels for easy mobility and you\'ll want to take it wherever you go! WHY BUY THE NEWAIR AF-320 DELUXE AIR COOLER??? How about these reasons - more air flow, built in air purifier, easy to move compact design, and one of the only units available with a water cooling pad that NEVER needs to be replaced! With all these features in mind, its easy to see why the Newair AF-320 and AF-330 are the best options for personal spot cooling. Moreover, you are purchasing an air cooler with built in safety features, a no hassle warranty, and a convenient remote control. ENJOY COOLING FOR UP TO 15 FEET AWAY!', 0.86, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41diJoEkhFL._SY300_.jpg', NULL),
(24, 'Dinosaur Triceratops Raptors Fantasy Wall Decor Art Print Poster (16x20)', 'Enhance your home decor instantly by grabbing this Dinosaur Triceratops Raptors Fantasy art print poster. It would look great when hung on the wall of your kid\'s bedroom. It will attract new generations of little ones. Hurry up and order this poster for its excellent quality with high degree of color accuracy.', 3.97, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/61fHJOJ5VTL._SY300_.jpg', 'Impact Posters Gallery'),
(25, 'KitchenAid KHM7T 7-Speed Artisan Hand Mixer, White', 'Pound for pound, a good hand mixer is perhaps the most laborsaving  kitchen device. While my grandmother relied on arm strength and force of will to  beat a stiff dough or to mash potatoes, a light and easily maneuvered hand mixer  saves time and muscles. This one from KitchenAid features seven-speed digital  touch control for precision mixing, and an electronic sensor that will adjust  the power as you go, so you maintain a steady mixing speed. If you\'re beating a  delicate batter, you can use the Soft Start feature and ease into faster speed.  When you\'re finished, the beaters are easily ejected. If you\'ve ever battled  heavy doughs, you\'ll appreciate the beaters\' design: they don\'t have a center  post, so dough won\'t collect in the middle of the beater and clog the machine.  It\'s also designed for easy cleaning.--Laura Cuthbert', 99.17, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/314FQRK1SSL._SX300_.jpg', 'KitchenAid'),
(26, 'George Lopez 11 x 17 TV Poster - Style A', 'George Lopez 11 x 17 TV Poster - Style A', 9.98, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51ktSoL1-9L._SY300_.jpg', 'MG Posters'),
(27, 'Silk Habotai Fitted Sheet - King - Ivory', 'The combination of unique silk weaves creates our new Dream Sheet Collection of Silk Bed Linens. Our Dream Collection utilizes specialized weaves for the individual linens in order to create the perfect blend of function and luxury. The Dream Collection, of course, incorporates impeccable details to construction and finishing quality. The silk satin flat sheet and silk satin pillowcases uses a satin weave that is soft, very smooth with a slight natural sheen and a drape that perfectly surrounds you with lightweight comfort. The silk habotai flat sheet uses a s simple box weave and sand wash finish that creates a subtle and soft texture. Please note that these silk bed linens are individually packaged pieces. If you would like a complete set, simple choose \"King Set\" or \"Queen Set\" when ordering. \"Sets\" will include 1 silk satin flat sheet, 1 silk habotai fitted sheet and 2 jumbo or 2 king satin pillowcases. Ordering by the \"set\" provides a 10% discount off the price if ordered separately. Dimensions: Oversize flat sheets: King: 110\" x 108\"; Queen: 94\" x 108\". Jumbo pillowcase: 21\" x 32\" fits both standard and Queen Pillow. King pillowcase: 21\" x 40\"', 215, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41QZtQlaS2L._SX300_.jpg', NULL),
