(30, 'Chic Charcoal Cream and Taupe Eternity Circles Comforter Set', 'Crescent Full Bed in a Bag - Multi (NEW in Original Packaging)Make the most of mid-century modern with this fabulous Crescent complete bedroom ensemble! Inspired by the geometric designs of the \'50s, the face of the comforter and the standard flanged pillow shams features an all over design of interlocking crescent shapes in chic hues of brick, persimmon, taupe and cream on a charcoal ground; the comforter reverses to a graduated, vertical stripe in the same shades. The 200-thread-count, 100% cotton sheets and pillowcases feature an all over textural pattern in cream and charcoal. All components are constructed of sumptuous, 100% cotton fabric and are machine washable. The Crescent complete bedroom ensemble retails for $119.99 in major department stores and upscale specialty shops!Bed in a Bag includes:One Full Comforter (80 in. W x 88 in. L)Two Standard Shams (20 in. W x 26 in. L)One Full Flat Sheet (81 in. W x 96 in. L)One Full Fitted Sheet (54 in. W x 76 in. x 15 in. pocket)Two Standard Pillowcases (20 in. W x 30 in. L)Comforter and Sham: 100% CottonSheet Set: 100% Cotton, 200 Thread CountMachine WashableImported', 4.32, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51i3AcX4dCL._SX300_.jpg', NULL),
(31, 'Architec Stretch Cooking Bands SCBMP , Set of 25', 'Award-winning cooking bands replace butcher twine or toothpicks and are made of 100% medical-grade, food-safe silicone. Freezer-safe and great when deep-frying, bands are heat resistant to 600F. Bands can be used in the oven, on the griddle, barbecue or rotisserie. Bands fit up to a 20-pound turkey, and colors are ideal for food identification: rare/medium/well, mild/medium/spicy. For extra length, just knot bands together. Re-use or dispose. Dishwasher safe. 2\". Set of 25.', 19.49, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41fhMxJ1rBL._SY300_.jpg', NULL),
