(40, '4 Silver Square Charger Plate 12.6&quot; Tempered Glass Micro/oven 350/dishwasher Safe', 'This set of 4 charger is made of shatter proof tempered glass. It is trimmed in gold. Beautiful when hosting a party or as a gift. \nTempered glass is one of two kinds of safety glass regularly used in applications in which standard glass could pose a potential danger. Tempered glass is four to five times stronger than standard glass and does not break into sharp shards when it fails. Tempered glass is manufactured through a process of extreme heating and rapid cooling, making it harder than normal glass.', 1.32, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41S2nNZ59JL._SY300_.jpg', NULL),
(41, 'Great Northern Commercial Quality 12 Hot Dog and 5 Roller Grilling Machine, 1000-Watt', 'The Great Northern Popcorn Company has created a masterpiece with their BIG DAWG Professional Hot Dog Machine. This is not a cheap knock off, it is the original machine and carries the Great Northern Popcorn Companys 1 year limited warranty. With the GNP your customers will not have to wait in long lines for a stale dog since GNPs exclusive slow roller system is guaranteed to keep each dog fresh, plump, and juicy until served. It is perfect for birthday parties, and is a hit at holiday cookouts, Super bowl parties, and just celebrating with family and friends. Need a larger or smaller machine? Check out our TOP DAWG and MAD DAWG commercial grillers as well. Quality/Durability: The GNP griller is used by convenience stores, mini-marts, gas stations, and concession stands across the country. It is made of industrial strength stainless steel and meets the toughest FDA standards for restaurant equipment. Again, this is the original GNP machine and carries the Great Northern Popcorn Companys 1 year limited warranty. Dont settle for 2nd best. PRODUCT SPECIFICATIONS: * Maximum Capacity: 18 Hot Dogs Per Batch (6 Rows of 3) * Premium Grade Cover for safety and cleanliness. Can be reversed as well. * Stainless Steel Design makes it Safe and Easy to Clean * 5 Premium Grade Non-Stick Stainless Steel Rollers * Heavy Duty Motor and Safety Temperature Control * Dual Temperature Controls: You can roast/cook on the front rollers while you keep the batch on the real rollers warm * Removable and Easy to Clean Stainless Steel Drip Tray * Full rotation rollers--not partial like the cheap imitations. * Heat Up and Keep Warm Control Modes * Easy to use with front ON-OFF switch * Skid Proof Rubber Feet for Tabletop Use * Built-in Fuse for Safety Purposes * Grill Dimension: 23 L by 13 W by 15 H * Tray size: 17-3/4 L by 7 W * Power: 1000-watt * 110V/50Hz * Full 1 Year Warranty * CE Approved', 16.22, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41JUj4kMxlL._SY300_.jpg', NULL),
(42, 'Hoover U5145-900 Tempo WidePath Bagged Upright Vacuum', 'Company is on the way! The doorbell could ring any minute, and you need to make just a few more frantic swipes with the vacuum before you can stash it away and answer the door unfettered. Ding! Dong! Maybe it\'s time for a Tempo WidePath vacuum from Hoover.The Tempo WidePath features a 15-inch cleaning path for super fast vacuuming when you need it the most. Plus, the Tempo WidePath cleans indoor air while you vacuum, thanks to an innovative allergen filtration system that traps 100 percent of dust mites, 99.98 percent of ragweed, and common grass pollens for cleaner breathing and fresher air. A powerful, 12 amp motor provides ample suction and doesn\'t leave anything behind. A brilliant headlight illuminates the cleaning path to ensure thorough vacuuming. Onboard tool storage keeps attachments, such as a dusting brush, furniture nozzle, crevice tool, and two extension wands in close reach. A smaller profile (approximately 33-1/4 by 18-1/2 by 9-1/2 inches) and lighter overall weight makes the Tempo WidePath easy to push, and easier to maneuver around and under furniture, too. And, your purchase is covered by a Hoover one-year warranty. Get a Tempo WidePath, and never get behind on the housework again.--Brian Olson', 13.8, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/31JFGHBGCCL._SY300_.jpg', NULL),
(43, 'Zeta Tau Alpha Zeta Tau Alpha pillowcases', 'These terrific Zeta Tau Alpha pillowcases fit a standard pillowcase and will liven up any dorm room. Comes with polka dot greek letters and mascot as shown.', 7.16, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41Y38ZVyqZL._SY300_.jpg', NULL),
(44, 'Winware 6 Quart Oval Stainless Steel Gold Accented Chafer', '6 Quart Oval Stainless Steel Gold Accented Chafer', 46.72, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41n%2BexTuokL._SY300_.jpg', 'Winware'),
(45, 'GB Eye Californian Camper Poster', 'This high quality poster image is approximately 36-Inch by 24-Inch and is suitable for framing. The poster offers a lower cost alternative to a more expensive print or painting. Posters are perfect wall d&#xE9;cor for any household or age range.', 7.58, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51aQknmeyuL._SY300_.jpg', 'GB Eye'),
(46, 'Norpro Egg/Mushroom Slicer', 'This is a charming model, not just because it\'s shiny enough to be raccoon bait, but because it seats well--the whole of the unit is neat and compact with an exceptionally sturdy base. The top of the hinged cutter raises and lowers smoothly, chopping mushrooms for omelets or slicing eggs for salads, garnishes, and hors d\'oeuvres with an economy of motion that requires minimal hand strength. Eggs rest securely in the oval-shaped nest and don\'t squirm about as you slice through. As a bonus, parents of youngsters may appreciate that the stainless-steel cutting wires make \"music\" when picked or strummed. By adjusting the Phillips-head screw, you can tighten the wires for more cutting control--or to change pitch. Yolk or mushroom particles may deposit in the wires, so rinse or hand wash immediately after use.--Carol Gnojewski', 6.74, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41C45SJMX0L._SX300_.jpg', 'Norpro'),
(47, 'French Bull Melamine Dessert Spoon, Ziggy, Set of 4', 'Stay ahead of the curve with a fresh look from French Bull. This Set of Four Melamine Dessert Spoons reinvents an everyday staple with its bright chevron design and versatile melamine construction. Made of high-grade, glazed melamine, this dessert spoon set is lightweight, non-absorbent and heat-resistant to 365-Degree F. Durability and shatter-resistance make it perfect for everyday use, indoor and outdoor entertaining, kid-friendly and dishwasher-safe. All pieces are non-toxic and BPA-free. Coordinate your look or playfully mix-and-match with French Bull\'s myriad other lively patterns and solids. French Bull: a fresh look for a contemporary lifestyle.', 11.4, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/419okrGnRTL._SY300_.jpg', NULL),
(48, 'Steve Silver 22 or 40 inch Avenue Lazy Susan Size - 40 inches', 'Heighten the elegance of your dining table with this frosted glass lazy susan. The Steve Silver Avenue Lazy Susan features a sleek round design with a stable base and an elevated turn table. The smooth swivel action makes it easy to turn the lazy susan and serve a variety of drinks or dishes to your guests. An exquisite centerpiece for any dining table, this lazy susan is available in 22- or 40-inch diameters. Sleek, elegant design for tabletop use. Choice of 22- or 40-inch diameter. Frosted glass with a subtle blue tint. Smooth swivel action. Fine-looking centerpiece for a dining table.', 200, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51Wg2jX0E4L._SX300_.jpg', 'Steve Silver'),
(49, 'Mahogany Rangoli Printed Rectangular Cotton Tablecloth, 60-Inch by 90-Inch', 'Floral sprays and flower designs in dark brown, orange and mustard on a dark rust background give a casual feel to this wonderful Rangoli cotton print pattern. The circle print on the contrasting orange border is fitted between dark brown floral bands of the rectangular tablecloth.', 0.57, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51ctNcEkCZL._SX300_.jpg', NULL),
(50, 'Heavy Duty 3-Plate Display Rack', 'Adorn your walls with plates that capture the imagination as well as your style with these easy to hang plate racks.', 23.69, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/31upfAySXsL._SY300_.jpg', NULL),
(51, 'Serta 4-Inch Dual Layer Mattress Topper, California King', 'If you\'d like to enjoy the ultimate in sleeping luxury, this Serta 4-inch Mattress Topper will provide unmatched comfort and support. It starts with a 2-inch pillow-top layer of fiberfill that surrounds you in softness. Below that there is a 2-inch layer of premium memory foam that helps eliminate painful pressure points, and evenly distributes body weight for a restful night\'s sleep. Open cell technology provides a temperature neutral sleep surface for cool comfort. The result is you sleep better and wake up feeling refreshed and rejuvenated. And besides all that, you\'ll add years of life to your mattress.', 188.99, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41m9WSTdPRL._SX300_.jpg', NULL),
(52, 'Zak Designs Disney Frozen Movie Melamine Plate, 8-Inch, Set of 6', 'Disney Frozen Movie 8-inch melamine Plates by Zak Designs comes in a set of six and is made of 100-percent melamine. Kids who love Disney\'s Frozen will love eating their meal off one of these cute and fun melamine plates. Parents will love the plates for the functionality and simplicity they bring to meal preparation. The plates are stain resistant, BPA free and top rack dishwasher safe; do not microwave. By Zak Designs, a company that offers a wide variety of high quality dinnerware, travel ware and products at the forefront of tabletop trends for contemporary and on-the-go lifestyles.', 5.09, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51sp7rXTDCL._SY300_.jpg', NULL),
(53, 'Melissa And Doug Bella Butterfly Placemat (Each)', 'Ready to set the table for delicious fun?! Charming Sunny Patch characters decorate the table and make meals and snacks more appealing! Everything is food- and dishwasher-safe.', 2, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51348GAsdAL._SY300_.jpg', 'Melissa &amp; Doug'),
(54, 'Norpro Mini Cutting Serving Tray, Green', 'Norpro\'s Mini Cutting Serving Tray.  Slice, dice, chop and prep food for pan or bowl.  Perfect size and shape for entertainment buffet or bar.  Raised sides contain juices from fruits, vegetables or meats and crumbs from bread and cheese. Also use to serve hors d\'oeuvres.   Nonstick, stain resistant and won\'t dull knives.  Nonslip, soft grip handle.  FDA approved.', 12.9, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/310DGGVEEDL._SY300_.jpg', 'Norpro'),
(55, 'Tropical Palm Tree 18 x 18&quot; Microsuede Beach Pillow - Botanical Vintage Coastal Decor', 'Made and designed In USA in our Florida Keys studio. Micro Suede pillow cover for the ultimate softness and huggability.&nbsp; This will be your favorite pillow. This microsuede tropical palm tree pillow is washable. &nbsp; The pocket design cover makes it easy to remove the cover and wash it on gentle cycle, air dry.&nbsp; You can actually use this pillow and it will continue looking like new !&nbsp; Practical and beautifull.', 11.29, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51JyTRLLjvL._SX300_.jpg', NULL),
(56, 'Coaster Shell and Leaf Sofa Table', 'This beautiful occasional group features a shell and leaf design in a deep brown finish.', 210.69, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/515ukcviUqL._SY300_.jpg', 'Coaster Home Furnishings'),
(57, '(2 Pack) Roasting / Cooling Rack Oval 12&quot; x 8&frac12;&quot;', 'This roasting rack allows one to roast their poultry or meat without touching the bottom of the pan. This is critical to roasting as this type of cooking refers to dry heat. Without using a roast pan, the poultry or meat would boil in its own juices. Using a roasting rack is also a healthy way to prepare roasts as it allows the fat to drip off the poultry and meat and rest under the rack.', 9.99, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/4144ZYjmanL._SX300_.jpg', NULL),
(58, 'Faux Fur Throw Blanket 58&quot; x 84&quot; - Black Mink - TR - New Arrivals', 'Thermal, keep you cozy and warm. Perfect for outdoor, watching TV. Stay warm this winter and feel great with this faux fur throw. Unbelievably soft and plush. Dynamic decor piece to throw over a couch or chair, it serves as a fashionable, functional accent piece. Perfect blanket to cuddle up on a chilly evening. Luxurious comfort of oversized faux-fur throw.', 89.5, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/61jnWhlEqML._SY300_.jpg', 'Best Home Fashion'),
(59, 'Woozie Wine Glass Koozie - The Chick\'s Pack of Funny Phrases', 'Words of Woozie - and in this case - Words to party or visit by!  Each one of the six have a different funny wine related saying.  Everyone you see will want one of these!  Use them to keep your favorite glass beverage cool.  Even if it\'s not wine, you can drink it out of a wine glass!', 38.7, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51MLAc0HxTL._SY300_.jpg', NULL),
(60, 'All In One Party Tray Snap On Lid Food Storage Serving', 'Hot or cold, savory or sweet, liven any get-together with your favorite treats! Special inserts elegantly serve snacks, baked treats, munchies and more; the convenient snap-on carry lid makes it perfect for taking to parties and potlucks. Dishwasher safe. Plastic. 14\" diameter x 4\" high.', 12.95, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51IPW89u1zL._SY300_.jpg', NULL),
(61, 'Huge 16 Inch Dog Cat Paw Print Stepping Stone Concrete Plaster Mold 1148', 'Huge dog cat paw print concrete plaster stepping stone mold.  This paw mold will make a finished piece that measures 16 inches across and is 1 3/4 inches thick.  This is a great size to use for making a walkway or creating paths through your garden area.  Be sure to check out our smaller sizes of paw molds to use along side this one.  This paw mold is a great piece to use for fund raisers or organizations to raise money.\n\nAll molds come with basic instructions for creating your pieces.  Molds are ideal for business or hobby use.  Our molds are made of several different blends of polyethylene plastic which allows you to use the molds over and over.  Our plastic is somewhat flexible so it allows for your finished pieces to be removed from the molds easily.  Our molds are a great way for you save money on that do it yourself project, create the finished look you want for pennies compared to what you would pay for these at a retail store.  Or maybe your looking at making some extra money and want to start your own business, we have lots of different molds to choose from.  Make your own patio pavers to decorative stepping stones as well as garden benches and downspouts we\'ve got you covered.  \n\nYou can use plaster, concrete, cement, mortar, resin and soap in all of our molds.  \n\nWe ship UPS and USPS - so please include a physical address to ship to if you have a po box as some packages could be shipped out UPS due to the size, weight and location.  Please note that international orders that shipping fees do not cover any additional charges that your country may declare as an import tax or fee once it enters your country.  Every country has different regulations and not all have additional fees but we want all international buyers to be aware prior to making their purchases.', 33, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41q7fnctQwL._SX300_.jpg', NULL),
(62, 'Your-Zone, Make a Splash Peva Shower Curtain, with Tote, 70&quot; x 71&quot; (Cool Dot)', 'Features a multi-colored polka dot design on a solid black body and measures 70\" X 71\", 100% PEVA, wipe with a damp cloth for easy care.', 24.99, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51MEcfD6OwL._SY300_.jpg', 'Your Zone'),
(63, 'Big Mouth Toys 40? So What? I Can Still Kick Your Ass! Can Hugger', 'You\'ve still got it, tough guy. Remind everyone that age is nothing but a number with our \"40? So What? I Can Still Kick Your Ass!\" can hugger.  Great gag gift and party favor for 40th birthday celebrations.  Keeps drinks cold and hands warm.  Holds one 12 oz. can.', 4.79, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/416xSLJvIxL._SY300_.jpg', NULL),
(64, '5 Piece University of Nebraska Collegiate Coaster Gift Set', 'VUNE-HA24 Features: -Cork-backed to protect furniture.-Made in the USA. Includes: -Includes: 4 coasters & 1 holder. Color/Finish: -Full color printing. Dimensions: -4.5\'\' H x 4.5\'\' W x 1.5\'\' D, 2 lbs.', 14.99, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/5128Yp2w3fL._SY300_.jpg', NULL),
(65, 'Bamboo Rough Hewn Natural Japanese Style Chopsticks, Set of 5', 'Rough hewn natural bamboo rustic Japanese style chopsticks. Set of 5 pairs in a cellophane sleeve. Chopsticks are 9.5 inches long with square handles and smooth square tips. Made in China.', 19.64, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41M6n7CcTAL._SX300_.jpg', NULL),
(66, 'Farberware Nonstick Bakeware 9-by-5-Inch Loaf Pan', 'A commonly requested size in recipes for yeast breads, quick breads, and pound cakes, this 9-inch by 5-inch loaf pan is also standard to many meat loaf recipes. Made of even heating carbon steel, the pan is designed for even browning. The pan has a nonstick coating to help you remove the bread from the pan with ease and make cleanup easy.', 6.96, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41MMpOpq81L._SY300_.jpg', 'Farberware'),
(67, 'Full 15&quot; Deep Cast Iron Heavy Duty 100% Cotton Zipper Mattress Cover', NULL, 1.38, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51VSuF2thlL._SY300_.jpg', NULL),
(68, 'Mother\'s Love Art Print Art Poster Print by Evita Tezeno, 24x30', 'Mother\'s Love Art Print is digitally printed on archival photographic paper resulting in vivid, pure color and exceptional detail that is suitable for any museum or gallery display. Finding that perfect piece to match your interest and style is easy and within your budget!', 12.39, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41qaR4pP-VL._SY300_.jpg', NULL),
(69, '3&quot; Piranha 4 Piece Herb Grinder - Silver', 'Our exclusive Piranha Grinders are compact and extremely durable. Diamond-cut teeth ensure precision grinding of all your favorite products. This is the perfect tool to go along with any vaporizer. Features and Details of the Piranha Grinder: Milled from High Quality Aluminum. Razor Sharp Teeth will shred the toughest aromatherapy blends with ease. Nylon gasket ensures smooth grinding action. Magnetic Lid helps prevent spillage. 3\" Diameter x 2\" High. Pollen Scraper Included! Piranha Carrying Pouch Included!One Year Warranty!', 30.79, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/31imFQ4buGL.jpg', NULL),
(70, 'Hunter 30035 HEPAtech Solo2 Air Purifier White', 'Like all Hunter products, the SOLO2 has been artfully designed to provide unmatched quality, style, and whisper quiet performance. Where it differs from Hunter\'s other Air Purifiers - besides its whimsical design - is in its application. The SOLO2 provides clean air where room air purification isn\'t possible. It\'s small enough to sit on a desktop in your home or work office, or compact enough to throw it in an overnight bag when you travel.\n\nMost air purifiers are designed to clean large areas, but sometimes that isn\'t practical. The SOLO2 was designed to create a clean zone of air in your personal breathing space. The SOLO2 removes airborne particles, allergens, and odors from the air passing through the filter and then directs the clean air into your personal breathing area. Being over 90% effective, it not only removes the things you can see - like dust - but more importantly those you can\'t.', 18.28, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41A-5yDcNiL._SY300_.jpg', NULL),
(71, 'Benson Mills Flow &quot;Spillproof&quot; 60-Inch by 84-Inch Fabric Tablecloth, Ivory', 'This elegant stainproof tablecloth utilizes the latest state-of-the-art technology to put an end to stains on your tablecloth.  All liquids, even wine, bead up so you can quickly wipe it clean with a sponge or napkin.', 17.29, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51D5nBMcTtL._SY300_.jpg', 'Benson Mills'),
(72, 'Oenophilia Winetag Cellar Set with Permanent Pen', 'Contains 100 Wine Tags with Permanent Pen. A necessity for all wine collectors and a subtle compliment as a gift. Reusable plastic WineTags identify red and white wines at a glance without disturbing them. To use on Champagne bottle, just snip the shoulder of tag.', 13.29, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/412Gf8tYYYL._SY300_.jpg', 'Oenophilia'),
(73, 'Home Dynamix CSB5-277 Cosmopolitan Bath 13-Piece Shower Curtain Set, Pink/Black', 'Home Dynamix has established it\'s self as one of the top leaders in pioneering and marketing the most exciting, innovative and value based bath products.&#xA0;They started in the New York metropolitan area and shortly thereafter, expanded on this success into the national and international arenas. Their bath collections offer modern designs and colors at an exceptional cost. The Cosmopolitan Bath Collection includes a shower curtain and 12 matching shower curtain rings.', 13.15, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51ncDMoOwfL._SY300_.jpg', 'Home Dynamix'),
(74, 'Amba RWP-CP Radiant Plug-In Curved Towel Warmer, Polished', 'Enjoy warm towels with the Radiant Hardwired Towel Warmer.  The Radiant towel warmer heats up quickly and has ten crossbars for optimal drying.  Made of 18/8 Stainless Steel, this towel warmer is available with a Brushed or Polished Stainless Steel finish and includes a matching cover plate.  Use the discreet on/off switch, or use an optional plug-in or wall-mounted 7 day/24 hour programmable timer', 175, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41fE3lPoakL._SY300_.jpg', 'Amba'),
(75, 'Circular Harmony Bright Red 18&quot;x18&quot; Decorative Silk Throw Pillow Cover', 'Bring new life to your living room, family room, or den with these hand made Thai silk blend pillow covers. These pillow covers are made from 70% Thai silk which gives them a luxurious shimmer and 30% polyester-just enough to allow for hand washing and make costly dry cleaning unnecessary. These pillows can even be pressed with a warm iron, if desired! Pillow covers measure 18\" x 18\" and require 18\" inserts (or recycle your old 18\" pillow).', 14.95, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51HBm7-ojqL._SY300_.jpg', NULL),
(76, 'DEVIL DOG RECRUITING STATION US MARINES UNITED STATES TANK CORPS WAR VINTAGE POSTER REPRO', 'THE POSTERS ARE PRINTED ON HEAVYWEIGHT PROFESSIONAL MATTE \nPAPER USING **GICLEE** TECHNIQUE. THE QUALITY OF THE IMAGES IS \nJUST AMAZING!!! 100% SATISFACTION GUARANTEE!!! IF YOU ARE NOT \nSATISFIED JUST RETURN THE POSTER, NO QUESTIONS ASKED!!! \n\nIMAGE SIZE IS 12\" X 16\" - PAPER SIZE IS 15\" X 18\" \n\nTHIS POSTER WILL MAKE A FANTASTIC ADDITION TO THE HOME DCOR!!! \n\n***HIGH QUALITY POSTER FOR DISCERNING CLIENTES!!!!!***', 7.9, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51eiIH7WBOL._SY300_.jpg', NULL),
(77, 'Catskill Craftsmen  Kitchen Roll-About Cart', 'Catskill Craftsmen has become the nation\'s leading manufacturer of ready-to-assemble domestic hardwood kitchen islands, carts, and work-centers. Catskill Craftsmen manufactured items are made from naturally self-sustaining, non-endangered North American hardwoods, primarily Northern Yellow Birch. Lumber is purchased from area sawmills, then dried, manufactured, and packaged on site. All sawdust, shavings and waste materials generated during the manufacturing process is converted into wood pellet fuel, and used to heat homes. This sturdy, attractive cart features a wide drawer, thick lacquered top, cherry stained base, two towel bars, two slatted shelves, and locking caster wheels.', 236.07, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51CCzJm-B9L._SY300_.jpg', 'Catskill Craftsmen'),
(78, 'Cuisinart DCC-1200PRC 12-Cup Replacement Glass Carafe, Black', '12-cup carafe with ergonomic handle, dripless spout, and knuckle guard. DCC-1200PRC is the black replacement carafe for the 12-cup Cuisinart Brew Central Coffeemaker.', 18.48, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41GTh25CjwL._SX300_.jpg', NULL),
(79, 'Heavy Duty Laundry Duffle Bag Color: Dark Purple', '3640141 Color: Dark Purple Features: -Material: Heavy duty polyester. -Stand up design converts into laundry hamper. -Stitched in shoulder straps and handles for easy transport. -Open top zipper design. -2 Exterior pockets for detergents/accessories. -Capacity: 25 gallons. -90 day manufacturer warranty.', 25.81, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41bbj-OvXqL._SY300_.jpg', 'Casual Home'),
(80, 'Homelegance 722PU-24 Parson Counter Height Chair, Black Bi-Cast Vinyl, Set of 2', 'This Sierra Collection Parson dining chair features standard 20\"SH chair (722PUS) and counter height 24\"SH chair (722PU-24). This ebony finished group in black bi-cast vinyl provides the style and function your space needs.', 230, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41SXnBQd6uL._SY300_.jpg', NULL),
(81, 'All-Clad 3-Piece Canister Storage Set', '3 Piece Canister Set complete with three attractively styled stainless steel and glass storage containers.', 14.76, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41YWH3R7R7L._SX300_.jpg', NULL),
(82, 'Northpoint Sapphire Twin Sherpa Blanket, Burgundy', 'This elegant blanket is super soft and supple to get you through the coldest nights. One side features a luxurious micro mink that breathes, while the other side offers a micro Sherpa material that instantly warms the body.', 34.99, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41DFpX%2BFvrL._SX300_.jpg', NULL),
(83, '(22x28) Fortitude Iwo Jima Motivational Poster Print', '(22x28) Fortitude Iwo Jima Motivational Poster Print', 1.72, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/413VcCo1zgL._SY300_.jpg', NULL),
(84, 'BIG SALE TODAY 50% OFF Premium Bamboo Kitchen Tools - 6 Piece Cooking Utensils Set - 20% Heavier Duty Than Other Wooden Utensil Accessories - &quot;No Hassle&quot; Warranty - Compare to OXO - Includes: Wooden Turner Spatula, Rounded Fork, Single Hole Mixing Spoon, Slotted Spatula, Slotted Spoon, Bamboo Spoon - 100% Satisfaction Guaranteed', 'The Perfect Accessories For Any Kitchen Lover!- No More Scratching Your Expensive Cookware- No More Melting Plastic Utensils In Your FoodWhether you are a professional cook or beginner cook, this 6-Piece Bamboo Cooking Utensil Set is a great prep tool for you.Present this cooking set to someone special or anyone who loves to cook as a wonderful housewarming or holiday gift.This wooden spoon and spatula tool set is easy to maintain. Simply wash with a mild soap and water solution, and dry thoroughly.- Highly Recommend For Use With Non Stick Cookware, Accessories and Grill Mats.Click The Yellow \"See All Buying Options\" Button Now Before They Are Gone. Supplies Are Extremely Limited.', 9.67, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41kj8zzxUJL._SX300_.jpg', NULL),
(85, 'Southern Champion Tray 09455 Clay Coated Kraft Paperboard White Non-Window Lock Corner Bakery Box, 8&quot; Length x 8&quot; Width x 5&quot; Height (Case of 100)', NULL, 32.97, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/21JdZOAhJ8L._SX342_.jpg', 'Southern Champion Tray'),
(86, 'Parrish Magic Line 3 Piece Mini Tier Mini Round Aluminum Cake Pan Set', 'Professional quality round cake pan made in the USA with heavy gauge aluminum', 20.23, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41EsD9I-nhL._SY300_.jpg', 'Parrish Magic Line'),
(87, 'Rio Home Fashions Hi-Lo Memory Incline Foam Mattress Topper/Pad, Twin', 'Rio home fashions hi-lo memory foam topper/pad has a 1-inch slab of memory foam bonded on a 1/2-inch 3-1/2-inch incline wedge of urethane foam. It is covered in a zippered circular knit cover that is washable. the memory foam top layer is sensitive to body temperature ad changes shapes as you move to provide responsive support all night long for better sleep. The pressure resistant base foam layer provides extra support. Upper body elevation during sleep may help alleviate problems associated with nasal congestion, snoring, constricted airways, heartburn/acid reflux and respiratory distress. Lower body/leg elevation may help alleviate swelling in legs, knees, ankles and feet. Made with hypoallergenic materials. Available in twin 38-inch by 74-inch , full 53-inch by 74-inch , queen 59-inch by 79-inch , king 76-inch by 79-inch and cal king 71-inch by 8-inch sizes.', 79.12, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/21wRKxKXc8L._SX300_.jpg', NULL),
(88, 'ProScale Moderno Digital Health Scale', 'ProScale Moderno Digital Scale with 330lb Capacity The ProScale Moderno is modern contemporary design personal digital scale built with advanced weighing technology! The thick, tempered glass platform and brushed stainless steel foot pads make for an interesting and sleek designed while supporting body weight and housing cutting edge electronics. What other scale has normal weighing modes, body fat measurement, and water weight weighing? The ProScale Moderno does it all, plus has ProScale\'s 5-year warranty! Available in STAINLESS STEEL only.', 4.23, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/414GZLecOVL._SY300_.jpg', NULL),
(89, 'Skylanders Giants Deluxe Lunch Bag', 'Ideal for the Skylanders fan in the house comes this ultra cool insulated lunch bag. Features BAC OFF technology that protects the interior lining from bacteria that causes odors and stains. Tested lead safe, PVC free, and phthalate free. Measures approximately 9 in (L) x 8 in (W) x 4 in (D).', 14.99, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/61NFiVotWPL._SY300_.jpg', NULL),
(90, 'Coaster Rustic White Metal Full over Full Bunk Bed', 'This Coaster White Metal Full over Full Bunk Bed is perfect for a college dorm or two siblings who share a room. A sturdy full size metal frame ensures that this bed will last for years to come. The contemporary style and bright white finish will match a variety of household d?cors. For a bed that combines space-saving practicality, affordability, durability, and attractive style, get the Coaster White Metal Full over Full Bunk Bed.  Features:    Full over full size bunk bed  Metal frame  White finish  Some assembly required  Mattresses sold separately    Specifications:    Overall Dimensions: 59\" H x 57\" W x 78.25\" D', 409.48, 'http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/51VDqiv8sfL._SY300_.jpg', 'Coaster Home Furnishings');
